《'''二嫫'''》是1994年出品的一部中国电影，由[[周曉文|周曉文]]导演，[[艾丽娅|艾丽娅]]主演。本片根据徐宝琦的同名小说改编而成，获瑞士第47届罗卡诺国际电影节青年评审团金奖、国际影评人奖、评审团大奖。<ref>Ye and Zhu<!--Indexed by the library of Congress as "Ye, Tan" and "Zhu, Yun"-->, p. [http://books.google.com/books?id=javqwyBe0WoC&pg=PA52&dq=Ermo+film&hl=en&sa=X&ei=l7tZUqjDFIj28wSS4YGwAg&ved=0CFAQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=Ermo%20film&f=false 52] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=javqwyBe0WoC&pg=PA52&dq=Ermo+film&hl=en&sa=X&ei=l7tZUqjDFIj28wSS4YGwAg&ved=0CFAQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=Ermo%20film&f=false |date=20140104154144 }}. "The film received the Swissair/Crossair Special Prize and the Prize of the Ecumenical Jury at the 1994 Locarno International Film Festival in Switzerland."</ref><ref>{{cite book | title=Historical Dictionary of Chinese Cinema | publisher=Rowman & Littlefield | year=2012 | isbn=0810867796}}</ref>

